parameters.name: MaxResults
parameters.description: The number of entries to return on each page. Default value: **50**.

parameters.name: NextToken
parameters.description: The token that determines the start point of the query.

parameters.name: Status
parameters.description:
The status of the route learning correlation. Valid values:

*   **Active**: available
*   **Enabling**: being enabled
*   **Disabling**: being disabled

parameters.name: TransitRouterAttachmentId
parameters.description: The ID of the network instance connection.

parameters.name: TransitRouterAttachmentResourceId
parameters.description: The ID of the network instance.

parameters.name: TransitRouterAttachmentResourceType
parameters.description:
The type of the network instance. Valid values:

*   **VPC**: virtual private cloud (VPC)
*   **VBR**: virtual border router (VBR)
*   **TR**: transit router
*   **VPN**: VPN connection

parameters.name: TransitRouterRouteTableId
parameters.description: The ID of the route table of the Enterprise Edition transit router.
